sourcesContent:
import styled from 'styled-components';

import Form from '../../UI/Form';

const RecipeFilterStyled = styled.div``;

const InputContainer = styled.div`
	padding: 0.8rem 0;
	width: 25rem;
`;

const Label = styled.label``;

const Input = styled.input`
	width: 100%;
	height: 2rem;
	margin-top: 0.5rem;
	padding-left: 0.5rem;
	border-radius: 0.2rem;
	outline: none;
`;

const Select = styled.select``;

function RecipeFilter() {
	return (
		<RecipeFilterStyled>
			<Form>
				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='sortRecipes'> Sort Recipes By </Label>
					<Input type='text' name='sortRecipes' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='intolerances'> Intolerances </Label>

					<input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>Dairy</Label>
					<input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>Gluten</Label>
					<input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>Peanut</Label>
					<input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>Sesame</Label>
					<input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>Seafood</Label>
					<input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>Shellfish</Label>
					<input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>Nuts</Label>
					<input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>Wheat</Label>
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='diets'> Diets </Label>
					<Select type='text' name='diets' multiple>
						<input type='checkbox' />
						glutenFree
						<input type='checkbox' />
						<Label>ketogenic </Label>
						<input type='checkbox' />
						<Label>vegetarian </Label>
						<input type='checkbox' />
						<Label>lactoVegetarian </Label>
						<input type='checkbox' />
						<Label>ovoVegetarian </Label>
						<input type='checkbox' />
						<Label> vegan</Label>
						<input type='checkbox' />
						<Label> pescatarian</Label>
						<input type='checkbox' />
						<Label> paleo</Label>
						<input type='checkbox' />
						<Label> primal</Label>
						<input type='checkbox' />
						<Label> lowFODMAP</Label>
						<input type='checkbox' />
						<Label>whole30 </Label>
					</Select>
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='minCal'> Min Calories </Label>
					<Input type='text' name='minCal' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='maxCal'> Max Calories </Label>
					<Input type='text' name='maxCal' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='minCarbs'> Min Carbs </Label>
					<Input type='text' name='minCarbs' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='maxCarbs'> Max Carbs </Label>
					<Input type='text' name='maxCarbs' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='minProtein'> Min Protein </Label>
					<Input type='text' name='minProtein' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='maxProtein'> Max Protein </Label>
					<Input type='text' name='maxProtein' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='minSugar'> Min Sugar </Label>
					<Input type='text' name='minSugar' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='maxSugar'> Max Sugar </Label>
					<Input type='text' name='maxSugar' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='minSodium'> Min Sodium </Label>
					<Input type='text' name='minSodium' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='maxSodium'> Max Sodium </Label>
					<Input type='text' name='maxSodium' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='minSatFat'> Min Saturated Fat </Label>
					<Input type='text' name='minSatFat' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='maxSatFat'> Max Saturated Fat</Label>
					<Input type='text' name='maxSatFat' />
				</InputContainer>
			</Form>
		</RecipeFilterStyled>
	);
}

export default RecipeFilter;
